THE GAME
--------

  'Lights' is a Workbench game that is played on a 10 x 10 board
filled with lightbulbs that are either turned on or off. The idea
is to switch on all the light bulbs on that board. You play by
clicking on a light bulb, which will toggle all the lights on the
same row and column from where the light bulb is located.

  When you complete a game board, Lights displays a new board,
with more lights that have been switched on or off, and so on...

  If you find that the game is too easy, you can try the 'Harder'
game by clicking on the 'Easy/Harder' toggle button...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

